semantic: A container for the status bar at the top of the screen. It holds elements like the time, battery indicator, and other system-level information.
A battery icon in the status bar, indicating the current battery level of the device.
A signal strength icon in the status bar, representing the current network connectivity status.
A Wi-Fi icon in the status bar, showing the current Wi-Fi connection status.
A text element in the status bar displaying the current time, '9:41'.
A container for the main header section of the UI, which includes location information, a search icon, a notification icon, and a headline text.
A search icon, allowing users to initiate a search action. It is visually placed in the header section.
A location pin icon, visually representing the user's current location.
A notification icon, allowing users to access notifications or alerts. It is located in the header section.
A circular button or icon, possibly representing a user profile or additional settings. It is located in the header section.
A text element displaying the label 'Your Location', indicating the section where the user's current location is shown.
A text element displaying the user's current location, 'New York City'. It is associated with the location pin icon.
A headline text element displaying the message 'Provide the best food for you', serving as a welcoming or promotional message for the user.
